imdb.plot outline: Ryan Serhant, star of "Million Dollar Listing New York," and his fiancée Emilia Bechrakis invite viewers to attend their wedding ceremony on the gorgeous Greek island of Corfu. But before they walk down the aisle, Ryan and Emilia must see to all of the preparations for their big day. With the wedding date quickly approaching, every last minute detail must be finalized as stress levels rise. Meanwhile, Ryan's "Million Dollar Listing" costar Luis D. Ortiz plans an unforgettable bachelor party.
